I need you to add a MicroStrategy migration planning layer to my existing Power BI PBIP/TMDL builder.

Goal:
Take messy MicroStrategy inputs — generated SQL, report details HTML/text, template fields, prompts, and optional PDF/image-derived visual metadata — and convert them into a standard JSON contract that my existing Power BI builder can consume.

Do not try to build a universal MicroStrategy translator. Build a deterministic triage + handler engine.

