  - GREEN_SQL_GRID
  - AMBER_SQL_WITH_WARNINGS
  - CHART_REPORT
  - DERIVED_METRIC_REVIEW
  - CUBE_OR_NO_SQL_REVIEW
  - UNSUPPORTED_COMPLEX
- Detect:
  - generated SQL exists
  - SELECT aliases
